<p>We’re thrilled to welcome you for a trial day at <strong><%= @hub.name %></strong> BGA Hub! This experience is designed to give <%= @visit.learner_name %> a genuine feeling of what it’s like to be a BGA learner, surrounded by our community and learning culture.</p>

